name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 24, Liu Qiangdong stated at an executive meeting that “Anyone who has poor long-term performance and never works hard is not my brother.”

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
May 24, Longyan, Fujian. A parent posted that her 13-year-old son was studying at Liannan Middle School.
On April 18, the child was stabbed multiple times by a classmate on the way home from school. Afterwards, the murderer said on QQ that he was "under 14 years old and would not go to jail."
The victim's family said that the perpetrator has returned to school.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On May 25, a fire broke out in the dormitory building of Communication University of China.
Students said that the smoke alarm did not sound when the fire broke out, and the upstairs escape passage and downstairs access control were locked and could not be accessed by face recognition. The fire extinguisher was broken, and all fire-fighting facilities were unusable, which almost led to a tragedy.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On the afternoon of May 25, in Ganzhou, Jiangxi, a bus broke through the fence at the roundabout at the south gate of Zhanggong District and fell onto the underground open-air platform. The casualties and the number of passengers on the bus are still being verified.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Due to the recent frequent suicides by jumping off bridges in Taiyuan, additional bridge guards have been deployed on many bridges in Taiyuan.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Some netizens found that Lai Qingde's related Weibo topics were banned

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On May 25, Anhui Hefei 2024 Housing Fair was held, and Anhui Provincial Party Committee Deputy Secretary and Governor Wang Qingxian visited the scene.
On the same day, owners of unfinished projects such as Runwangyun, Jianfa Feicui Yunjing, Poly, and Lianfa Binhu Tingyu collectively defended their rights at the housing fair.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: It was reported on May 25 that Wang Wenbin, deputy director of the Information Department of the Chinese Ministry of Foreign Affairs and spokesperson, will reportedly step down and may be sent abroad as an ambassador or transferred to other important positions.

content:

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: May 24, Shenqiu, Henan. The local urban management officers clashed when they forcibly demolished a gas station in Dawanglou Administrative Village that had been run by the family of martyrs for decades and had complete procedures.
